PRESIDENT John Magufuli has extended the time for Tanzania Tourism Board (TTB) to three years. According to a statement released by the Chief Secretary , John Kijazi, the Head of State has extended the time for the board with effect from April 23, this year. The board is chaired by Judge (rtd) Thomas Mihayo. Other members include Augustine Kungu Olal, Zabein Muhaji Mhita, Richard Rugimbana, Mark Leveri, Ally Hussein Laay and Ibrahim Mussa.